ottom-large:0px;--awb-spacing-left-large:0px;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:0px;--awb-spacing-left-medium:0px;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:0px;--awb-spacing-left-small:0px;"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column"><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-1 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-highlight fusion-loop-off fusion-highlight-double_underline fusion-title-size-two" style="--awb-text-color:#000000;--awb-highlight-top-margin:15px;--awb-margin-top:45px;--awb-margin-bottom:60px;--awb-margin-top-small:10px;--awb-font-size:38px;" data-highlight="double_underline"><h2 class="fusion-title-heading title-heading-center fusion-responsive-typography-calculated" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;--fontSize:38;line-height:1.5;"><span class="fusion-highlighted-text-prefix"></span> <span class="fusion-highlighted-text-wrapper"><span class="fusion-highlighted-text" style="color:#000000;">欣派简介</span></span> <span class="fusion-highlighted-text-postfix"></span></h2></div></div></div><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-2 fusion_builder_column_1_2 1_2 fusion-flex-column" style="--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:50%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:0px;--awb-margin-bottom-large:0px;--awb-spacing-left-large:0px;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:0px;--awb-spacing-left-medium:0px;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:0px;--awb-spacing-left-small:0px;"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column"><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep" style="align-self: center;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:25px;margin-bottom:25px;width:100%;"></div><div class="fusion-image-element " style="text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);"><span class=" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-2 hover-type-none"><img decoding="async" width="400" height="552" src="/original/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020090309483026.jpg" data-orig-src="/original/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020090309483026.jpg" alt class="lazyload img-responsive wp-image-15325" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%27400%27%20height%3D%27552%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%20400%20552%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%27400%27%20height%3D%27552%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E" data-srcset="/original/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020090309483026-200x276.jpg 200w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2020090309483026.jpg 400w" data-sizes="auto" data-orig-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 400px" /></span></div></div></div><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-3 fusion_builder_column_1_2 1_2 fusion-flex-column" style="--awb-padding-top:25px;--awb-padding-right:25px;--awb-padding-bottom:25px;--awb-padding-left:25px;--awb-overflow:hidden;--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-box-shadow:0px 25px 25px 0px rgba(58,58,58,0.3);;--awb-border-color:rgba(202,157,115,0.68);--awb-border-top:6px;--awb-border-style:solid;--awb-border-radius:10px 10px 10px 10px;--awb-width-large:50%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:0px;--awb-margin-bottom-large:0px;--awb-spacing-left-large:0px;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:0px;--awb-spacing-left-medium:0px;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:0px;--awb-spacing-left-small:0px;"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column"><div class="fusion-text fusion-text-1"><p>欣派包装起步于1997年，从最初的包装袋开始做起，最先进军的是美国市场，经过近五年的辛苦耕耘，我们在美国地区拥有了一批长久合作的品牌客户。</p>
<p>继而到了2003年，公司开始逐步布局，着手进军欧洲市场，那里的品牌文化和底蕴更强。凭借着在美国地区所积累的丰富经验。在欧洲的市场开拓，没有像在美国市场初期的时候那么困难，当然，也遇到了很多挫折(在此不在赘述)。举一个简单的，欧盟的标准和美国的检测标准是完全不一样的。这一做就是24年，经过这些年的发展，我们的工厂一步一步的扩大了，从最初的10几人，到如今的100多人，从三间作坊，到如今的1万平方，从最初的手工折纸，到如今的机械自动化。</p>
<p>科技在发展，欣派也在进步，在改变。不变的是我们对品质的把控，对产品的负责，对工艺水准与技术的自信。这些年我们在欧美地区我们合作过很多一线奢侈品牌，凭借着我们严格的要求和奢侈品牌包装定制经验，我们在国内同样也拥有了很多知名品牌。从初次合作的质疑到长久合作的信任。</p>
<p>包装产品追根究底就是做品牌营销，只有做好才能得到客户的认可，得到市场消费者的青睐。如果你现在对自己的包装不满意，对品质方面不满意，不妨联系下欣派，行与不行，全当交个朋友。</p>
</div></div></div><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-4 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column" style="--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:0px;--awb-margin-bottom-large:0px;--awb-spacing-left-large:0px;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:0px;--awb-spacing-left-medium:0px;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:0px;--awb-spacing-left-small:0px;"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column"><div class="fusion-flip-boxes flip-boxes row fusion-columns-4 flip-effect-classic"><div class="fusion-flip-box-wrapper fusion-column col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3"><div class="fusion-flip-box flip-right" tabindex="0"><div class="flip-box-inner-wrapper"><div class="flip-box-front"><div class="flip-box-front-inner"><h2 class="flip-box-heading">资质认证</h2>FSC, SEDEX, GRS, ISO9001</div></div><div class="flip-box-back"><div class="flip-box-back-inner"><h3 class="flip-box-heading-back">包装工厂资质</h3>
<p>欣派包装常年为欧美奢侈品牌提供包装盒制作服务, 资质齐全的包装盒供应商, 拥有多项欧盟相关认证资质. 如:FSC森林环保认证, Sedex供应商商业道德认证, 奢侈品牌第二方验厂报告, ISO-9001, GRS可持续发展…</p>
</div></div></div></div></div><div class="fusion-flip-box-wrapper fusion-column col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3"><div class="fusion-flip-box flip-right" tabindex="0"><div class="flip-box-inner-wrapper"><div class="flip-box-front"><div class="flip-box-front-inner"><h2 class="flip-box-heading">生产车间</h2>机器设备,人工设施,工厂配置</div></div><div class="flip-box-back"><div class="flip-box-back-inner"><h3 class="flip-box-heading-back">包装工厂设备</h3>
<p>工厂占地17000平方米,员工100余人.完善的生产体系. 三所生产车间,多条生产线同时工作,生产流程规范一体化. 自动化生产设备,自动裱糊成型机,红外线视觉定位,烫金, 覆膜, 压纹, 印刷等工艺. 更有完善的品检体系.</p>
</div></div></div></div></div><div class="fusion-flip-box-wrapper fusion-column col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3"><div class="fusion-flip-box flip-right" tabindex="0"><div class="flip-box-inner-wrapper"><div class="flip-box-front"><div class="flip-box-front-inner"><h2 class="flip-box-heading">欣派历程</h2>创业历程, 工作态度，用户群体</div></div><div class="flip-box-back"><div class="flip-box-back-inner"><h3 class="flip-box-heading-back">工厂历程与态度</h3>
<p>欣派包装自1997年开始供应包装贸易出口，从最初的美国市场，辐射到欧洲，到如今在各个大洲都有着稳定的客户群体。作为一家包装纸盒制作工厂,我们秉承着严谨的态度与制作水准.为客户提供高质量产品为己任。</p>
</div></div></div></div></div><div class="fusion-flip-box-wrapper fusion-column col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3"><div class="fusion-flip-box flip-right" tabindex="0"><div class="flip-box-inner-wrapper"><div class="flip-box-front"><div class="flip-box-front-inner"><h2 class="flip-box-heading">欣派设计</h2>原创包装, 结构设计, 开发能力</div></div><div class="flip-box-back"><div class="flip-box-back-inner"><h3 class="flip-box-heading-back">包装结构与设计</h3>
<p>欣派拥有强大的开发能力,对于复杂的工艺与结构拥有自己的独特的见解. 自发制作设计了多款原创包装,欣派设计师自08年上海美院毕业后一直从事绘画设计相关工作, 具过硬功底. 在包装上沉浸式的设计受到众多客户关注.</p>
</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-5 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column" style="--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:0px;--awb-margin-bottom-large:0px;--awb-spacing-left-large:0px;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-spacing-right-medium:0px;--awb-spacing-left-medium:0px;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-spacing-right-small:0px;--awb-spacing-left-small:0px;"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column"><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-2 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="--awb-text-color:#000000;--awb-margin-top:20px;--awb-margin-bottom:20px;--awb-font-size:30px;"><h2 class="fusion-title-heading title-heading-center fusion-responsive-typography-calculated" style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0;font-size:1em;--fontSize:30;line-height:1.5;">资质认证</h2></div></div></div><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-6 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column" style="--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:10px;--awb-spacing-right-large:0px;--awb-margin-bottom-large:0px;--awb-spacing-left-large:0px;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:0px;--awb-spacing-left-medium:0px;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:0px;--awb-spacing-left-small:0px;"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column"><div class="fusion-tabs fusion-tabs-1 classic nav-is-justified horizontal-tabs icon-position-left mobile-mode-accordion" style="--awb-title-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-title-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-title-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-title-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-alignment:start;--awb-inactive-color:#f1f2f2;--awb-background-color:#ffffff;--awb-border-color:#e2e2e2;--awb-active-border-color:#ca9d73;"><div class="nav"><ul class="nav-tabs nav-justified" role="tablist"><li class="active" role="presentation"><a class="tab-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-f67811acbc367153737" aria-selected="true" id="fusion-tab-fsc" href="#tab-f67811acbc367153737"><h4 class="fusion-tab-heading">FSC</h4></a></li><li role="presentation"><a class="tab-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-ee33692603abc7cbe0b" aria-selected="false" tabindex="-1" id="fusion-tab-sedex" href="#tab-ee33692603abc7cbe0b"><h4 class="fusion-tab-heading">Sedex</h4></a></li><li role="presentation"><a class="tab-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-2630b09f62f5aeb2d66" aria-selected="false" tabindex="-1" id="fusion-tab-iso-9001" href="#tab-2630b09f62f5aeb2d66"><h4 class="fusion-tab-heading">ISO-9001</h4></a></li><li role="presentation"><a class="tab-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-7bb0a29adc4a86630a1" aria-selected="false" tabindex="-1" id="fusion-tab-iso-140001" href="#tab-7bb0a29adc4a86630a1"><h4 class="fusion-tab-heading">ISO-140001</h4></a></li><li role="presentation"><a class="tab-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-42921d281a4cb83d670" aria-selected="false" tabindex="-1" id="fusion-tab-ecovadis可持续发展评级" href="#tab-42921d281a4cb83d670"><h4 class="fusion-tab-heading">EcoVadis可持续发展评级</h4></a></li><li role="presentation"><a class="tab-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-2d09dcd2281536f7242" aria-selected="false" tabindex="-1" id="fusion-tab-lvmh验厂审计报告" href="#tab-2d09dcd2281536f7242"><h4 class="fusion-tab-heading">LVMH验厂审计报告</h4></a></li><li role="presentation"><a class="tab-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-f5f2c6f18fbed048707" aria-selected="false" tabindex="-1" id="fusion-tab-奢侈品牌验厂报告" href="#tab-f5f2c6f18fbed048707"><h4 class="fusion-tab-heading">奢侈品牌验厂报告</h4></a></li></ul></div><div class="tab-content"><div class="nav fusion-mobile-tab-nav"><ul class="nav-tabs nav-justified" role="tablist"><li class="active" role="presentation"><a class="tab-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-f67811acbc367153737" aria-selected="true" id="mobile-fusion-tab-fsc" href="#tab-f67811acbc367153737"><h4 class="fusion-tab-heading">FSC</h4></a></li></ul></div><div class="tab-pane fade fusion-clearfix in active" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="fusion-tab-fsc" id="tab-f67811acbc367153737">
<p><img decoding="async" class="lazyload alignnone size-full wp-image-26434 aligncenter" src="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008305775.webp" data-orig-src="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008305775.webp" alt="欣派包装fsc认证证书" width="417" height="550" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%27417%27%20height%3D%27550%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%20417%20550%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%27417%27%20height%3D%27550%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E" data-srcset="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008305775-200x264.webp 200w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008305775-227x300.webp 227w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008305775-400x528.webp 400w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008305775.webp 417w" data-sizes="auto" data-orig-sizes="(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px" /></p>
<p>森林管理委员会(Forest Stewardship Council)缩写FSC，是一个非政府、非营利组织。它成立于1993年，其发起者为国际上一些希望阻止森林遭到不断破坏的非政府机构、环保人士、木材贸易组织及具有社会责任感的消费者等。</p>
<p>纸张的来源就是通过木制品，FSC通来追踪木制品从森林到消费者的整个过程，从而可以控制木材的合法及可持续来源。所以对环保有要求的公司，都会要求包装盒厂家拥有对应的资质。使林区的作业结构和经营能够更加合理，确保经营者在获取利润的同时，不以牺牲森林资源、生态系统为代价，欣派包装从事纸质品的包装盒和手提袋定制，在纸张的来源上，也是非常注重，一直注重着环保包装。</p>
</div><div class="nav fusion-mobile-tab-nav"><ul class="nav-tabs nav-justified" role="tablist"><li role="presentation"><a class="tab-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-ee33692603abc7cbe0b" aria-selected="false" tabindex="-1" id="mobile-fusion-tab-sedex" href="#tab-ee33692603abc7cbe0b"><h4 class="fusion-tab-heading">Sedex</h4></a></li></ul></div><div class="tab-pane fade fusion-clearfix" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="fusion-tab-sedex" id="tab-ee33692603abc7cbe0b">
<p><img decoding="async" class="lazyload alignnone size-full wp-image-26433 aligncenter" src="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/202208300830557.webp" data-orig-src="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/202208300830557.webp" alt="欣派包装Sedex认证证书" width="417" height="550" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%27417%27%20height%3D%27550%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%20417%20550%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%27417%27%20height%3D%27550%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E" data-srcset="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/202208300830557-200x264.webp 200w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/202208300830557-227x300.webp 227w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/202208300830557-400x528.webp 400w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/202208300830557.webp 417w" data-sizes="auto" data-orig-sizes="(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px" /></p>
<p>Sedex是一家全球性的供应商道德信息交换平台，众多世界知名品牌对供应商的要求均有此项，是世界上广泛使用的社会审核责任流程。<br />
也是全球公认可用于评估供应链的方式之一，包括劳动权利、健康与安全、环境和商业道德方面的评估。</p>
<p>欣派包装一直按照社会责任标准来要求自己。我们通过了Sedex验厂表明我们是遵守商业道德规范的、可以更放心和企业合作。我们的职工能够在良好的环境下进行工作，在生产包装盒与手提袋的时候能够更加尽心尽力的去工作，为客户完成更加精致的产品包装盒，产出高品质的产品。</p>
</div><div class="nav fusion-mobile-tab-nav"><ul class="nav-tabs nav-justified" role="tablist"><li role="presentation"><a class="tab-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-2630b09f62f5aeb2d66" aria-selected="false" tabindex="-1" id="mobile-fusion-tab-iso-9001" href="#tab-2630b09f62f5aeb2d66"><h4 class="fusion-tab-heading">ISO-9001</h4></a></li></ul></div><div class="tab-pane fade fusion-clearfix" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="fusion-tab-iso-9001" id="tab-2630b09f62f5aeb2d66">
<p><img decoding="async" class="lazyload alignnone size-full wp-image-26435 aligncenter" src="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/202208300830587.webp" data-orig-src="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/202208300830587.webp" alt="欣派包装ISO-9001认证证书" width="417" height="550" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%27417%27%20height%3D%27550%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%20417%20550%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%27417%27%20height%3D%27550%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E" data-srcset="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/202208300830587-200x264.webp 200w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/202208300830587-227x300.webp 227w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/202208300830587-400x528.webp 400w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/202208300830587.webp 417w" data-sizes="auto" data-orig-sizes="(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px" /></p>
<p>ISO-9001是由全球第一个质量管理体系标准 BS 5750（BSI撰写）转化而来的，是迄今为止世界上最成熟的质量框架。ISO 9001不仅为质量管理体系，也为总体管理体系设立了标准。它帮助各类组织通过客户满意度的改进、员工积极性的提升以及持续改进来获得成功。</p>
<p>欣派包装顺利的通过了ISO-9001质量认证管理体系。证实欣派包装具有能力提供满足顾客要求和适用的法规要求的产品包装盒与手提袋。所生产定制的包装盒和手提袋的质量得到根本保证。</p>
</div><div class="nav fusion-mobile-tab-nav"><ul class="nav-tabs nav-justified" role="tablist"><li role="presentation"><a class="tab-link" data-toggle="tab" role="tab" aria-controls="tab-7bb0a29adc4a86630a1" aria-selected="false" tabindex="-1" id="mobile-fusion-tab-iso-140001" href="#tab-7bb0a29adc4a86630a1"><h4 class="fusion-tab-heading">ISO-140001</h4></a></li></ul></div><div class="tab-pane fade fusion-clearfix" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="fusion-tab-iso-140001" id="tab-7bb0a29adc4a86630a1">
<p><img decoding="async" class="lazyload alignnone size-full wp-image-26436 aligncenter" src="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008305943.webp" data-orig-src="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008305943.webp" alt="欣派包装ISO-14001认证证书" width="417" height="550" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%27417%27%20height%3D%27550%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%20417%20550%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%27417%27%20height%3D%27550%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E" data-srcset="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008305943-200x264.webp 200w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008305943-227x300.webp 227w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008305943-400x528.webp 400w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008305943.webp 417w" data-sizes="auto" data-orig-sizes="(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px" /></p>
<p>ISO-9001是由全球第一个质量管理体系标准 BS 5750（BSI撰写）转化而来的，是迄今为止世界上最成熟的质量框架。ISO 9001不仅为质量管理体系，也为总体管理体系设立了标准。它帮助各类组织通过客户满意度的改进、员工积极性的提升以及持续改进来获得成功。</p>
<p>欣派包装顺利的通过了ISO-9001质量认证管理体系。证实欣派包装具有能力提供满足顾客要求和适用的法规要求的产品包装盒与手提袋。所生产定制的包装盒和手提袋的质量得到根本保证。</p>
