<p><img decoding="async" class="lazyload alignnone size-full wp-image-26437 aligncenter" src="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008310152.webp" data-orig-src="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008310152.webp" alt="欣派包装EcoVadis可持续认证证书" width="417" height="550" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%27417%27%20height%3D%27550%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%20417%20550%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%27417%27%20height%3D%27550%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E" data-srcset="/original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008310152-200x264.webp 200w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008310152-227x300.webp 227w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008310152-400x528.webp 400w, /original/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022083008310152.webp 417w" data-sizes="auto" data-orig-sizes="(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px" /></p>
<p>EcoVadis 提供供应商可持续性评级，并评估其全球供应商的 ESG 表现。它考虑了一系列企业社会责任问题，分为四个主题：“环境”、“劳工与人权”、“道德”和“可持续采购”。</p>
<p>欣派包装公司通过了优秀的评价分数。进行了多方面、多维度的评价。</p>
